#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.inline_asm_elementwise"
msgstr "# triton.language.inline_asm_elementwise"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:4
msgid "`inline_asm_elementwise` 用于在Triton内核中执行内联汇编代码，实现对张量的逐元素操作。"
msgstr "`inline_asm_elementwise` is used to execute inline assembly code within a Triton kernel, enabling element-wise operations on tensors."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.inline_asm_elementwise(asm, constraints, args, dtype, is_pure, pack, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `asm` | `str` | 必需 | 要执行的汇编代码，必须匹配目标平台的汇编格式 |\n"
"| `constraints` | `str` | 必需 | LLVM格式的汇编约束条件 |\n"
"| `args` | `tensor` | 必需 | 输入张量，其值会传递给汇编块 |\n"
"| `dtype` | `dtype` / `Sequence[dtype]` | 必需 | 返回张量的元素类型（可以是单个类型或类型元组） |\n"
"| `is_pure` | `bool` | 必需 | 如果为True，编译器假设汇编块没有副作用 |\n"
"| `pack` | `int` | 必需 | 每次内联汇编调用处理的元素数量 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `asm` | `str` | Required | The assembly code to execute, must match the target platform's assembly format |\n"
"| `constraints` | `str` | Required | LLVM-format assembly constraints |\n"
"| `args` | `tensor` | Required | Input tensors whose values are passed to the assembly block |\n"
"| `dtype` | `dtype` / `Sequence[dtype]` | Required | Element type of the returned tensor (can be a single type or a tuple of types) |\n"
"| `is_pure` | `bool` | Required | If True, the compiler assumes the assembly block has no side effects |\n"
"| `pack` | `int` | Required | Number of elements processed per inline assembly call |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:14
msgid "### 2.2 类型支持"
msgstr "### 2.2 Type Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:16
msgid ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ |×|   ✓  | × | × | ×  |\n"
msgstr ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | × | ✓ | × | ✓ | × | × | × |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:18
msgid "Ascend 对比 GPU 的输入张量类型 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp16、 fp64 、bf16 、bool的支持能力。"
msgstr "Ascend compared to GPU lacks support for input tensor types uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, fp16, fp64, bf16, and bool."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:20
msgid "### 2.3 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.3 Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:22
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_asm_add(x_ptr,\n"
"               y_ptr,\n"
"               output_ptr,\n"
"               n_elements,\n"
"               BLOCK_SIZE: tl.constexpr,\n"
"               ):\n"
"    pid = tl.program_id(axis=0)\n"
"    block_start = pid * BLOCK_SIZE\n"
"    offsets = block_start + tl.arange(0, BLOCK_SIZE)\n"
"    mask = offsets < n_elements\n"
"    x = tl.load(x_ptr + offsets, mask=mask)\n"
"    y = tl.load(y_ptr + offsets, mask=mask)\n"
"    output = tl.inline_asm_elementwise(\n"
"        asm=\"\"\"\n"
"        ADD.s64 $0, $1, $2\n"
"        \"\"\",\n"
"        constraints=(\n"
"            \"=l,l,l\"\n"
"        ),\n"
"        args=[x, y],\n"
"        dtype=tl.int64,\n"
"        is_pure=True,\n"
"        pack=1,\n"
"    )\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr + offsets, output, mask=mask)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:24
msgid "## 3. 语义GAP"
msgstr "## 3. Semantic Gap"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Inline_Assembly/inline_asm_elementwise.md:26
msgid ""
"1.内联汇编的寄存器仅支持`int64(s64)` 和`float32(f32)`。\n"
"2.约束限制仅支持`l`。\n"
"3.目前仅支持输入一维张量，计算高维张量需展开。\n"
msgstr ""
"1. The registers for inline assembly only support `int64(s64)` and `float32(f32)`.\n"
"2. Constraint restrictions only support `l`.\n"
"3. Currently, only one-dimensional tensors are supported for input; computing high-dimensional tensors requires flattening.\n"

